text: Fear of the Dark is a studio album by Iron Maiden. It went on sale on 11 May 1992. It was the most popular album in the United Kingdom when it started being sold. The album got mixed reviews. One person who reviewed it said that it was a "return to form," but had too many songs that were boring on it. ==Musicians== * Bruce Dickinson – vocals, bass guitar * Dave Murray – guitar * Janick Gers – guitar * Steve Harris – bass guitar, backing vocals * Nicko McBrain – drums ==Track listing== ==References== Category:Iron Maiden albums Category:1992 albums
